@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qgxxdi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v2 + wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.58)))
    v1 = v1
    v2 = (tmp - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.42) + (tmp + 0.71 - v1 + 0.22)))
    tmp = 0.34
    data[tid] = v0
